@prefix tab: <https://w3id.org/iladub/tab#> .
@prefix ex:  <https://example.org/tab-demo#> .
@prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .

# A PivotedDimension missing onAxis -> violates PivotedDimensionShape (onAxis minCount 1).
ex:dimBroken a tab:PivotedDimension ;
    tab:dimensionName "Quarter" ;
    tab:atLevel 0 ;
    tab:hasDimensionValue "Q1" ;
    tab:hasDimensionValue "Q2" .
